optimized_sql: WITH filtered_dates AS (SELECT d_date_sk, d_date FROM date_dim WHERE d_week_seq IN (SELECT d_week_seq FROM date_dim WHERE d_date IN ('2001-06-06','2001-09-02','2001-11-11'))), sr_items AS (SELECT i_item_id AS item_id, SUM(sr_return_quantity) AS sr_item_qty FROM store_returns JOIN filtered_dates ON sr_returned_date_sk = d_date_sk JOIN item ON sr_item_sk = i_item_sk GROUP BY i_item_id), cr_items AS (SELECT i_item_id AS item_id, SUM(cr_return_quantity) AS cr_item_qty FROM catalog_returns JOIN filtered_dates ON cr_returned_date_sk = d_date_sk JOIN item ON cr_item_sk = i_item_sk GROUP BY i_item_id), wr_items AS (SELECT i_item_id AS item_id, SUM(wr_return_quantity) AS wr_item_qty FROM web_returns JOIN filtered_dates ON wr_returned_date_sk = d_date_sk JOIN item ON wr_item_sk = i_item_sk GROUP BY i_item_id) SELECT sr_items.item_id, sr_item_qty, sr_item_qty / (sr_item_qty + cr_item_qty + wr_item_qty) / 3.0 * 100 AS sr_dev, cr_item_qty, cr_item_qty / (sr_item_qty + cr_item_qty + wr_item_qty) / 3.0 * 100 AS cr_dev, wr_item_qty, wr_item_qty / (sr_item_qty + cr_item_qty + wr_item_qty) / 3.0 * 100 AS wr_dev, (sr_item_qty + cr_item_qty + wr_item_qty) / 3.0 AS average FROM sr_items, cr_items, wr_items WHERE sr_items.item_id = cr_items.item_id AND sr_items.item_id = wr_items.item_id ORDER BY sr_items.item_id, sr_item_qty LIMIT 100
